# Cowork skills: vendored Anthropic skills (docx/xlsx/pptx/pdf/skill-creator) and _archive
# stay untracked; author-owned juridical skills ARE versioned so the daemon's boot-time
# `git pull` syncs them across Macs (Mac principal ↔ Mac Mini).
.claude/skills-cowork/*
!.claude/skills-cowork/SKILL_ALIASES.json
!.claude/skills-cowork/_shared/
!.claude/skills-cowork/analise-audiencias/
!.claude/skills-cowork/citacao-depoimentos/
!.claude/skills-cowork/citacoes-seguras/
!.claude/skills-cowork/classify-document/
!.claude/skills-cowork/criminal-comum/
!.claude/skills-cowork/dpe-ba-pecas/
!.claude/skills-cowork/estudo-dpe/
!.claude/skills-cowork/execucao-penal/
!.claude/skills-cowork/institucional/
!.claude/skills-cowork/juri/
!.claude/skills-cowork/linguagem-defensiva/
!.claude/skills-cowork/noticias/
!.claude/skills-cowork/numeracao-oficios/
!.claude/skills-cowork/oficio-gratificacao/
!.claude/skills-cowork/oficio-redacao/
!.claude/skills-cowork/pergunte-ao-auto/
!.claude/skills-cowork/protocolar/
!.claude/skills-cowork/schedule/
!.claude/skills-cowork/transcrever-atendimento/
!.claude/skills-cowork/transcrever-audiencia/
!.claude/skills-cowork/vvd/
!.claude/skills-cowork/analise-acordao/
# Lixo dentro das skills versionadas (artefatos Finder, backups) segue ignorado
.claude/skills-cowork/**/Icon?
.claude/skills-cowork/**/*.bak
*.docx

# Scripts temporários de diagnóstico/investigação (convenção: prefixo `_`)
scripts/_*.ts
scripts/_*.js

